    <h1 class="specialH1">Our Mission &amp; Vision</h1>
<h5 class="specialH5">Our Mission is to ruthlessly make sustainable periods easy. <br /> <br /> Our vision is threefold:</h5>
<br />
<h6 class="specialH6">​Environmental</h6>
<div style="font-size: 18px; text-align: center; padding-left: 50px; padding-right: 50px; line-height: 35px;">To give everyone the opportunity to access environmentally friendly products.</div>
<br />
<h6 class="specialH6">Social</h6>
<div style="font-size: 18px; text-align: center; padding-left: 50px; padding-right: 50px; line-height: 35px;">To work towards ending period poverty, increase quality menstrual hygiene education, and break down social barriers surrounding menstruation, using business for social good.</div>
<br />
<h6 class="specialH6">Economic</h6>
<div style="font-size: 18px; text-align: center; padding-left: 50px; padding-right: 50px; line-height: 35px;">To accelerate our growth and create sustainable economic opportunities for our stakeholders, while cultivating an environment for employees to excel and continuously advance.</div>
<br />
<h5 class="specialH5">Why Ruth?</h5>
<br />
<div style="font-size: 18px; padding-left: 50px; padding-right: 50px; line-height: 35px;">The name Ruth is special to us because we wanted to pay tribute to Ruth Bader Ginsburg, a powerful role model who fought for justice, equality, and female empowerment. RBG stood for women equality and fought her way to try and eliminate social injustices. We, at Ruth, are ruthlessly fighting with you to save the Earth one sustainable product at a time. <br /><br /> Ruth is also a symbol of generosity and kindness - in alignment with our goals of giving back to the women, girls, and people who menstruate, in most need of menstrual products. Together, let’s solve period poverty one menstrual pad at a time. <br /><br /> We want to make sustainable periods easy, and we hope you can join us.</div>
<div style="font-size: 18px; padding-left: 50px; padding-right: 50px; line-height: 35px;"><br /> Root for you. Ruth for you.</div>
